          com.retrogui.dualrpc.client.net.NonValidatingSSLSocketFactory
public class NonValidatingSSLSocketFactory
extends javax.net.ssl.SSLSocketFactory

Nonvalidating socket factory. The key store is passed in by the caller which permits loading from an alternate location such as the classpath or from within a jar.
